ore":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<br />\n之前有件物理畜開post但唔比問症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1819b87d29aa5b4bb432a2e3bfa24aa62176eec8","tid":2512764,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"盤骨前傾可以點搞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d992e4a4a6ed4ebedb0656dac293a5ed6c69acd","tid":2512764,"uid":208296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:25:34.000Z","msg":"慣性拗柴可以點搞？ 照過 mri, 淨係話ligament thick dd, 無咩問題，但我真係覺得成日拗"},{"pid":"e7c5623abb550900f0fab66bbb2ac89708aa08cb","tid":2512764,"uid":134062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a1bc1307f18ed7d358d407561b41fae2b29f59","tid":2512764,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"啪骨/正骨係咪物理治療？有無科學根據？<br />\n醫唔醫到寒背？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"啪骨係唔會可以啪返正 只係一個都市傳說 <br />\n<br />\n你地成日啪骨所聽到既聲 好多人以為係「啪返入位」 其實係錯 啪骨果下聲最主要係我地關裡裡面 synovial fluid 內既 gas bubble release 左先會有啪 一聲<br />\n<br />\n咁你可能問點解啪完會鬆咁多 其實 啪果下 我地個關節會腥signal 比個腦 做 neurostimulation 再腥返signal 比個關節周圍 令佢放鬆<br />\n<br />\n好似啪手指咁 其實你每90-120分鐘就可以啪到一次 咁唔通你手指每90-120分鐘就移一次位咩<br />\n<br />\n近十年既research 普遍都係 運動&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; any passive treatments (如香港人普遍認識既 啪骨 針灸 超聲波 laser magnetic theory electrotherapy etc)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啪骨係唔會根治到任何野 咁你可能會問 點解我仲會做 原因係啪完佢會有兩三日舒服返好多 我地就係想客人透過兩三日既舒適 去做返運動 增加返自信心 從而有利康復"},{"pid":"70f50dbe89804f1d7abae75b44767c98b18b5112","tid":2512764,"uid":134062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c0c35802454f2b1fb4645fe457fe2b33d3bbc9b","tid":2512764,"uid":154373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<br />\n之前有件物理畜開post但唔比問症<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor